{"tid":1742464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"響poly被狗登記嘅手足快D飛去另一個國家申請政治庇護","createTime":"2019-11-20T21:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T22:35:10.000Z","uid":212246,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"65ccbc3597e4405bfbd3a0659c8a7c601342192d","tid":1742464,"uid":212246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:10:35.000Z","msg":"冇錢嘅去咗台灣先，雖然台灣冇難民法，但係一定唔會送中/送返香港。滯留一段時間之後會送去加拿大或者其他有難民法嘅國家。<br />\n有錢D嘅申請eta，填好張basis of claim form飛去加拿大響機場申請，<br />\nlink for eta: <a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/visit-canada/eta/facts-zh-cantonese.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fimmigration-refugees-citizenship%2Fservices%2Fvisit-canada%2Feta%2Ffacts-zh-cantonese.html&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=7ed0c57c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/visit-canada/eta/facts-zh-cantonese.html</a><br />\nbasis of claim form: <a href=\"https://irb-cisr.gc.ca/en/forms/Documents/RpdSpr0201_e.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Firb-cisr.gc.ca%2Fen%2Fforms%2FDocuments%2FRpdSpr0201_e.pdf&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=16d6d3b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://irb-cisr.gc.ca/en/forms/Documents/RpdSpr0201_e.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n飛去美國都得，但係要等簽證。入境時交填好咗嘅I-589 form遞交申請。最好響加州入境。<br />\nI-589 form: <a href=\"https://www.uscis.gov/i-589\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscis.gov%2Fi-589&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=5bd33775\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.uscis.gov/i-589</a><br />\nuseful link: <a href=\"https://usahello.org/zh/resources/apply-for-asylum/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fusahello.org%2Fzh%2Fresources%2Fapply-for-asylum%2F&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=2b74bdf2\" target=\"_blank\">https://usahello.org/zh/resources/apply-for-asylum/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好飛去澳洲，澳洲係會將D難民丟入難民營。<br />\n<br />\n德國都係一個好選擇，佢地響魚蛋革命嘅時候收留咗黃台仰。另一個好處係可以唔使申請任何文直接入境。入咗境要之後去當地嘅BAMF office申請。<br />\nuseful link: <a href=\"https://www.dw.com/en/how-to-apply-for-asylum-in-germany/a-18723501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhow-to-apply-for-asylum-in-germany%2Fa-18723501&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=919547e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dw.com/en/how-to-apply-for-asylum-in-germany/a-18723501</a><br />\n<br />\n同中國關係惡化得好犀利嘅瑞典都可以一試: <a href=\"https://www.migrationsverket.se/English/Private-individuals/Protection-and-asylum-in-Sweden/Applying-for-asylum/How-to-apply-for-asylum.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.migrationsverket.se%2FEnglish%2FPrivate-individuals%2FProtection-and-asylum-in-Sweden%2FApplying-for-asylum%2FHow-to-apply-for-asylum.html&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=28fb7ec0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.migrationsverket.se/English/Private-individuals/Protection-and-asylum-in-Sweden/Applying-for-asylum/How-to-apply-for-asylum.html</a>"},{"pid":"fdb1b377ce2b586e263101cb79ef42a5940098fd","tid":1742464,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:12:08.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"980f46c1370e2ad635656112abaf37062119be84","tid":1742464,"uid":37081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:18:33.000Z","msg":"德國都要入難民營"},{"pid":"41a8b3f9ebb0bbb5d241381d74c3413808abba42","tid":1742464,"uid":212246,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:19:47.000Z","msg":"想申請成功嘅話最重要嘅一點係interview要誠實同無所不言。被拘留虐待嘅話講哂究竟發生咗D咩事，要平鋪直敘，唔好有任何誇大或者遺漏。<br />\n同埋佢有一點好重要，記得要買<strong>雙程機票</strong>，單程機票有機會俾狗咬。<br />\n行李記得pack返雙程機票中間嘅日數相應嘅衫褲鞋襪。<br />\n兩張機票中間嘅日數一定要夠合理，例如唔好去美國淨係去三日兩夜。歐美逃走路線嘅起碼中間要有兩至三個星期。"},{"pid":"b43a8e58c15a98a7f62e7eb8dc0d2aaab287a96c","tid":1742464,"uid":212246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"980f46c1370e2ad635656112abaf37062119be84","tid":1742464,"uid":37081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:18:33.000Z","msg":"德國都要入難民營"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:22:50.000Z","msg":"但係起碼唔會困咗響境外嘅島，澳洲難民係困哂響個叫Naruru嘅島，叫天不應叫地不聞"},{"pid":"fc329e3aa5d9a4d421eeb7664565011acd072d3b","tid":1742464,"uid":310534,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc688df82ea06dfd865a11051c301fe6742bd4e8","tid":1742464,"uid":125193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87326544d508f6dbe4705d7039c63e57bf82009f","tid":1742464,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ca484a9fddc870679780be1b43256f553d4d5b","tid":1742464,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65ccbc3597e4405bfbd3a0659c8a7c601342192d","tid":1742464,"uid":212246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:10:35.000Z","msg":"冇錢嘅去咗台灣先，雖然台灣冇難民法，但係一定唔會送中/送返香港。滯留一段時間之後會送去加拿大或者其他有難民法嘅國家。<br />\n有錢D嘅申請eta，填好張basis of claim form飛去加拿大響機場申請，<br />\nlink for eta: <a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/visit-canada/eta/facts-zh-cantonese.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fimmigration-refugees-citizenship%2Fservices%2Fvisit-canada%2Feta%2Ffacts-zh-cantonese.html&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=7ed0c57c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/visit-canada/eta/facts-zh-cantonese.html</a><br />\nbasis of claim form: <a href=\"https://irb-cisr.gc.ca/en/forms/Documents/RpdSpr0201_e.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Firb-cisr.gc.ca%2Fen%2Fforms%2FDocuments%