re":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:42:44.000Z","msg":"登記左重走到咩"},{"pid":"dc1f017651ab0a5b521eb94cd14bcadd0d2e741d","tid":1742464,"uid":212246,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4b6a3a7d75edc754d659ea61b52e553390fc446e","tid":1742464,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:42:44.000Z","msg":"登記左重走到咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:44:09.000Z","msg":"有D人係有登記但係冇拘捕。"},{"pid":"fdec6d6a6bf38fc8cde63de6752b366018cede6f","tid":1742464,"uid":51215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65ccbc3597e4405bfbd3a0659c8a7c601342192d","tid":1742464,"uid":212246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:10:35.000Z","msg":"冇錢嘅去咗台灣先，雖然台灣冇難民法，但係一定唔會送中/送返香港。滯留一段時間之後會送去加拿大或者其他有難民法嘅國家。<br />\n有錢D嘅申請eta，填好張basis of claim form飛去加拿大響機場申請，<br />\nlink for eta: <a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/visit-canada/eta/facts-zh-cantonese.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fimmigration-refugees-citizenship%2Fservices%2Fvisit-canada%2Feta%2Ffacts-zh-cantonese.html&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=7ed0c57c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/visit-canada/eta/facts-zh-cantonese.html</a><br />\nbasis of claim form: <a href=\"https://irb-cisr.gc.ca/en/forms/Documents/RpdSpr0201_e.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Firb-cisr.gc.ca%2Fen%2Fforms%2FDocuments%2FRpdSpr0201_e.pdf&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=16d6d3b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://irb-cisr.gc.ca/en/forms/Documents/RpdSpr0201_e.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n飛去美國都得，但係要等簽證。入境時交填好咗嘅I-589 form遞交申請。最好響加州入境。<br />\nI-589 form: <a href=\"https://www.uscis.gov/i-589\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscis.gov%2Fi-589&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=5bd33775\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.uscis.gov/i-589</a><br />\nuseful link: <a href=\"https://usahello.org/zh/resources/apply-for-asylum/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fusahello.org%2Fzh%2Fresources%2Fapply-for-asylum%2F&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=2b74bdf2\" target=\"_blank\">https://usahello.org/zh/resources/apply-for-asylum/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好飛去澳洲，澳洲係會將D難民丟入難民營。<br />\n<br />\n德國都係一個好選擇，佢地響魚蛋革命嘅時候收留咗黃台仰。另一個好處係可以唔使申請任何文直接入境。入咗境要之後去當地嘅BAMF office申請。<br />\nuseful link: <a href=\"https://www.dw.com/en/how-to-apply-for-asylum-in-germany/a-18723501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhow-to-apply-for-asylum-in-germany%2Fa-18723501&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=919547e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dw.com/en/how-to-apply-for-asylum-in-germany/a-18723501</a><br />\n<br />\n同中國關係惡化得好犀利嘅瑞典都可以一試: <a href=\"https://www.migrationsverket.se/English/Private-individuals/Protection-and-asylum-in-Sweden/Applying-for-asylum/How-to-apply-for-asylum.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.migrationsverket.se%2FEnglish%2FPrivate-individuals%2FProtection-and-asylum-in-Sweden%2FApplying-for-asylum%2FHow-to-apply-for-asylum.html&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=28fb7ec0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.migrationsverket.se/English/Private-individuals/Protection-and-asylum-in-Sweden/Applying-for-asylum/How-to-apply-for-asylum.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:47:43.000Z","msg":"咪撚去瑞典 諗都唔好諗<br />\n<br />\n第一瑞典要住係難民營架 <br />\n<br />\n第二，瑞典係唔會理你係香港人 <br />\n一律當你中國人，所以如果佢唔批你難民身份，佢係會帶你去中國領事館，會幫你買air china機票返香港<br />\n<br />\n識得有個朋友難民申請衰左 要比人送去中國領事館同要遣返 之後佢爬鐵絲網離開左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋歐盟地區申請難民 fail 左就10年之內冇得再apply 諗清楚好"},{"pid":"cc10b62f78a28d7475d747885d2dcb61bbe9951b","tid":1742464,"uid":19218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:49:55.000Z","msg":"一場理大戰 失去左上千義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d2a5f4082fd64552cdf253b54336613e2f39da","tid":1742464,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:52:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1ed99b45e4b613bfec9ba835587898762e0b6952","tid":1742464,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T21:57:45.000Z","msg":"靜靜地贏"},{"pid":"0673736ea9dc8ccfe692d44e1d42ef8dbed5af3f","tid":1742464,"uid":273804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:35:10.000Z","msg":"delete post please!!<br />\n<br />\n咪L害死人，要走嘅自然識搵路！！<br />\n<br />\n你咁樣同係poly將個逃生圖share去公海有咩分別！！"}]}